for seeing you!

376
00:27:44,343 --> 00:27:47,141
What's the matter? And where
should you be kept?

377
00:27:47,546 --> 00:27:50,014
You are in the train but you don't
know where the train is going!

378
00:27:50,282 --> 00:27:52,011
You get down on some
unknown station!

379
00:27:52,084 --> 00:27:53,949
Then you drive the car
like a crazy <i>man...</i>

380
00:27:54,019 --> 00:27:56,954
