in the dark lanes!

382
00:28:01,960 --> 00:28:04,485
Alone! In the lanes of Ratlam!

383
00:28:05,297 --> 00:28:07,959
What is your problem? Tell me!

384
00:28:09,101 --> 00:28:10,159
Sorry! Sorry! Sorry!

